Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:23.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:44.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前这冷酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理无从寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仅有肮脏的抢与夺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一场派对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命运纵横交错的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向着终点一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论胜者或败者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或许某物已然疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑问为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:23.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切尽皆消失在这片虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}现在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高举这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}来吧  继续BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:44.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束缚  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们只需变得疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需变得疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦或地狱  GO CRY GO
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:17.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}破滅さえ　厭わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:35.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ねえ、まだこの手に残る欠片だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:44.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}貴方のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:51.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}何もかも　失くしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}捧げるものが　在るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:03.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}未来だって　命でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:14.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}焼け尽きた感情も　不毛な祈りも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:19.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}縋る無様も　貢ぐ愚かも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:26.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}病んだ声も　穢れた両手も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:35.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}傷で裂かれた心も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:17.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}连毁灭  都不曾厌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:35.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}听我说  这依旧留在手中的残片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:44.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}也是属于你之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:51.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}即便失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}依旧要拿出奉献之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:03.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}无论是未来  亦或生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:14.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}还有燃尽的感情  和无谓的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:19.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}和狼狈的纠缠  和愚昧的供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:26.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}和病态的声音  和污秽的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:35.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}与这受伤撕裂的心
